description: Submission of reserved matters in respect of siting, design and external appearance pursuant to conditions 01, 02 and 03 of approved under Ref: TP/04/2623 for redevelopment of site involving erection of 185 residential units (comprising 6 houses and 179 apartments), incorporating 72 affordable housing units,  in 2, 3 and 4 storey buildings together with provision of a community facility with associated car parking, accessed from Ordnance Road and Kinetic Crescent being Phases 3 & 4 of redevelopment of Plots 4 & 5.
